<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,929,2034]" pageId="1" pageNumber="64">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,345,1037,1062]" pageId="1" pageNumber="64">Description.</emphasis>
Measurements, respectively male/female: body length, 
<number box="[982,1064,1037,1062]" pageId="1" pageNumber="64" value="3.6" valueMax="3.7" valueMin="3.5">3.5–3.7</number>
